info.long_name: Average Download Speed
info.description: Average download speed weighted by number of devices.
info.statement: The average download speed is {value} MB/s in {features.name}.

info.long_name: Number of devices
info.description: The number of unique devices accessing Ookla Internet speed tests.
info.statement: There are {value} unique devices in {features.name} accessing Ookla Internet speed tests.

info.long_name: Average Upload Speed
info.description: Average upload speed weighted by number of devices.
info.statement: The average upload speed is {value} MB/s in {features.name}.

info.long_name: Digital Equity Index
info.description: Relative equity of digital access, with 0 being a score of relative equity and 100 being relative inequity.
info.statement: The digital equity index for {features.name} is {value}.

info.long_name: Percent of the Internet-Connected Population with Fast Internet Speed
info.description: Percent of the internet-connected population with a fast internet speed (above 100/20 MB/s, able to stream HD video on multiple devices or download large files quickly).
info.statement: {value} percent of the internet-connected population in {features.name} has a fast internet speed.

info.long_name: Percent of the Internet-Connected Population with Good Internet Speed
info.description: Percent of the internet-connected population with a good internet speed (above 25/3 MB/s, able to stream video or online game for one device).
info.statement: {value} percent of the internet-connected population in {features.name} has a good internet speed.
